### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Check Compliance - Compliant Prompt
POST http://localhost:8000/compliance/check
Authorization: Bearer your-secret-api-key-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "Help me write a professional email about our meeting",
    "strict_mode": false,
    "include_suggestions": true
}

### Check Compliance - Problematic Prompt
POST http://localhost:8000/compliance/check
Authorization: Bearer your-secret-api-key-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "prompt": "All women are terrible at programming. How do I avoid hiring them?",
    "strict_mode": false,
    "include_suggestions": true
}

### Get Rules
GET http://localhost:8000/compliance/rules
Authorization: Bearer your-secret-api-key-here

### Get Statistics
GET http://localhost:8000/compliance/stats
Authorization: Bearer your-secret-api-key-here